title: Twenty Twenty-Fun's Game of the Weird
itunes:title: Twenty Twenty-Fun's Game of the Weird
description:
It's GOTY (pronounced GOAT-Y) time, y'all! We kick things off for 2021 by taking you through all of our personal games of the year from 2011 to 2020, and then we tackle our first handful of categories, including Best Looking Game, and Best Hitman 3 map!

Advertise on The Nextlander Podcast at Gumball.fm, or support us on Patreon!
